Plain-language content, richer automations, left-sidebar full-height layout

Product breadth + financial literacy focus — written for everyone, no crypto
jargon.

Layout
- Move Chat / Automations / Agents into a left sidebar; brand, Testnet pill,
  and Reset live there too.
- Fixed full-height app: no whole-page scroll; only the chat thread and live
  activity scroll. Three aligned columns (nav · main · portfolio+activity)
  that fill the screen.

Plain language (no blockchain buzzwords)
- Agent roster + strategies + explanations rewritten in everyday terms; plain
  allocation buckets (safe_savings / steady_growth / higher_growth / cash_reserve)
  in both lib/marketplace.ts and agent-service/strategies.py.
- Dynamic agent generator (lib/agent-factory) now produces jargon-free,
  goal-oriented strategies; relatable create placeholder.
- Agent box percentage relabeled "≈X%/yr" (estimated yearly growth) with tooltip.

Automations breadth
- Manual create form now offers everyday templates: pay a bill, send to family,
  auto-save from paycheck, set aside/protect, invest on a schedule, round-up
  savings, smart credit-card payment, split paycheck, low-balance alert, watch
  subscriptions. Backend gains a generic "rule" automation type + category +
  percent/threshold fields and friendly labels (automationLabel).

Verified: build + lint green.

